    "MissionGiver": "Covalex Independent Contractors",
    "Title": "Med. Distance Covalex Delivery Nyx",
    "TitleKey": "Covalex_Delivery_Nyx_Medium_Title_001",
    "Description": "Hi,\n\nPretty straightforward this one - We've got a bunch of stuff that needs moving through Nyx and need a competent contractor with a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> and a ship that can carry <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4>.\n\nDetails are attached. Good luck out there!\n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)\n\nElla Tieno\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping\n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
    "DescriptionKey": "Covalex_Delivery_Nyx_Medium_Desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hi,\n\nPretty straightforward this one - We've got a bunch of stuff that needs moving through Nyx and need a competent contractor with a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> and a ship that can carry <EM4>1 SCU cargo containers</EM4>.\n\nDetails are attached. Good luck out there!\n\n[Contractor|SignOff]\n\nElla Tieno\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping\n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
